clickingMost.java:2260: reached end of file while parsing }→ ^

means, You have just blown your load, Clean up time. }[/quote]

Not even close…

clickingMost.java:652: orphaned case case 9167: ^
Means the case is outside of a switch statement.

clickingMost.java:2260: reached end of file while parsing }→ ^
Means that the compiler was parsing your code and was expecting a closing brace but reached the end of the file instead.
